creat new env and do the next steps:
1- pip install Django
2- django-admin startproject project_name
3- cd project_name
4-python manage.py startapp app_name
5-python manage.py makemigrations
6-python manage.py migrate
7-python manage.py runserver

to actvate the admin do next steps:
1-python manage.py migrate
2-python manage.py createsuperuser
3-python manage.py runserver
4-In your web browser, go to http://localhost:8000/admin/. You should see the Django admin login page.
